Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已叫妳不要加入軍隊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是軍屬呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.76,0:14:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加入了吉翁軍並為沙比家復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出不合理的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳想好哥哥是那程度的男人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.87,0:14:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方是...誰來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.11,0:14:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聲音是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真巴拿魯所告訴我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.65,0:14:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是真正的事也不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那人的口頭禪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸的吉翁大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何要做出吉翁皇國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是為了新類型人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.70,0:15:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類未來而想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我突然因病而倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.94,0:15:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那群人中，爸爸已作好打算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.85,0:15:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我成為下期的少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也清楚知道吉翁大人的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被狄京哥指名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.13,0:15:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因自己去告訴狄京哥去暗殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如不這樣，爸爸的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會相繼的被打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連凱斯巴爾大人和阿爾黛西亞大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也裝上假的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.47,0:15:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如不是就不能在地球自由生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入去吉翁國，並進入高校和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍官學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是因想接近沙比家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.96,0:16:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我也有點成為了大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要沙比家把聯邦打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類新的和平是不需的發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.67,0:16:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新類型人的誕生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因阿姆羅是新類型人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新類型人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如把那新類型人作為敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不會有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.72,0:16:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後是要選擇手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.49,0:16:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真巴拿魯告訴了你新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.99,0:16:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是改變全體人類的理想類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.49,0:16:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如這樣，應不用把新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.46,0:16:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為敵人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱斯巴爾哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.57,0:16:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥你在想什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.47,0:16:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已說過會選擇手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿爾黛西亞會從木馬下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬？那白色基地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還留下從這裡逃走到地球的金塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球一生好好生活吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已不是妳所想知道的哥哥了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道為何要帶上頭盔吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已把過去拋棄了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿爾黛西亞，可否讓我看多次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本面目嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來改過吧！哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很漂亮呀！阿爾黛西亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.18,0:17:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不適合戰爭，從木馬下來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥，凱斯巴爾哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱斯巴爾哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特！布萊特，怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.93,0:17:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雜音很利害呢！         是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.97,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人擔心呢！阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱斯巴爾哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥...哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了，全部也被弄壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.60,0:18:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？是沒看過的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是白色基地的Vanni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！在這裡呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，雪拉好像發現了阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不能動，用運輸機吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！立即出發吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.69,0:18:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.72,0:18:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現了敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.92,0:18:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵機的沙自巴魯從港口出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？中止運輸機的出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用白色基地直接去收回鋼彈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.71,0:18:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬積蘭類型一台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口氣去突破吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐，在德薩斯發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.81,0:19:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，我也有悲哀的事呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可否不要問嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因拉拉的關係，蓋古克也能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回收了，對不起呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵方只得一台，好好的瞄準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即要求白色基地來援手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前，等待著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！米萊，出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到沙自巴魯的港口進行追擊戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第三閘門附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.78,0:20:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捕捉到發訊物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是爆炸物嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道，只是非常細小東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.98,0:20:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這緊急的時候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫鋼加農去調查吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，好像不是爆炸物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.06,0:20:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是普通的垃圾，垃圾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.50,0:20:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,域奇司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.44,0:20:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞那傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太遲了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.27,0:21:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,域奇司令...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在手提箱中放入的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只知道抬頭人是雪拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.76,0:21:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安姆羅也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜到是誰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.57,0:21:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.74,0:21:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖我有檢查的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但可否告訴我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手提箱內裡的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和寄出人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.84,0:21:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手提箱內裡的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.38,0:21:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想一定是金塊來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有錯的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是...寄出人是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.12,0:22:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞，是紅色彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.73,0:22:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會...沒可能的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.90,0:22:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的決定，我會實現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.47,0:22:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給溫柔的阿爾黛西亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.27,0:22:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱斯巴爾哥哥，包含了愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.89,0:22:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.80,0:22:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱斯巴爾哥哥，凱斯巴爾哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.63,0:22:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，不！是阿爾黛西亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自懂性以來，一直向住哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.44,0:22:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的身影，這樣的去大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.58,0:22:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管哥哥有型態或是沒有的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.75,0:23:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在叫了嗎？凱斯巴爾哥哥

